{"type": "article", "id": 36989, "title": "Dior 的设计师跳槽，以及，最近流行这种奇怪的牛仔裤 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-19T02:56:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1192, "name": "Alexander McQueen"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 2506, "name": "牛仔裤"}, {"id": 4999, "name": "三宅一生"}, {"id": 6372, "name": "米兰男装周"}, {"id": 9254, "name": "Bobbi Brown"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170119103803zf2nRhrSPA58Mp9g.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13522973/carven-names-serge-ruffieux-creative-director/\"><strong>Dior 前设计师 Serge Ruffieux 离职，加入 Carven 任创意总监</strong></a> | 出生于瑞士的 Serge Ruffieux 在 2008 年起加入 Dior 担任主设计师一职。Ruffieux 也曾为 Moschino 和 Sonia Rykiel 效力，加入 Carven 之后，他最快将带来 2018 年春夏系列的设计。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/bobbi-brown-new-business-ventures-10753785/\"><strong>Bobbi Brown 要创立新品牌</strong></a> | 去年年底，Bobbi Brown 离开了她一手创办的同名彩妆品牌，我们也曾报道过这个消息。近日，Bobbi Brown 宣布回归独立化妆师的身份，重新创立新的品牌，不过，她没透露更多关于新品牌的细节。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/alexander-mcqueen-2017-fall-winter-lookbook\">Alexander McQueen 正式发布 2017 秋冬系列</a>，新系列华丽且复古。以“孔雀”图案作为主要意象，通过暗红、大地色、宝蓝和墨绿等复古色调的运用，展现了文艺复兴时代的格调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103430M5XaozIWhBuRVsdP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103430wZ32LgXQzWqYMHCm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103430RJhUuMAeBQ1pVWYT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103431mVaHC6QexB90PcXS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103431hWiwp014LStIxHJ7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103431VC0eXJx9RpZSsz6H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103317xqYMrQc6IzJAbo38.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103317fkUPNqr3hSb56F7X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701191033177NFE63CcouY8ZgaI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103318Mwv2layUYunohrLc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103318JxwnvYlF82tSe0iQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103318SAwRELYm2G79qPrf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103318JSZ7noEsg4qv3lXM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103318RNdju3spSHlzan1D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103318fK54iCMJya6q8xlb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>推荐一个做日系服装的英国品牌。<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/story-mfg-2017-aw-lookbook\">STORY mfg 的 2017 秋冬新品</a>中，将日本传统的布料、色彩和复古洗水等元素，加以 oversized 的现代剪裁，充满了浓厚的日式风情。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103237lsgpEDaFh7NcMHxw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701191032372WbE3anpmx9GiH5k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103237ewWxS6RfA7laDQUb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103237fACINGx7dyQOiq9j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103238vsQVIFJ8hOi7Nmny.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017011910323804HhBblaWmDJQSzP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103237su4DmOfaq3Jc0XrQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103238TlzLwh2OdujQv14P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103251iTykL1VBX9C064FZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103251OL7NiPlZujatYr8q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103251ukIvlQFPoBCnmLcK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103251om7t3YrGHuyxX5gh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103301sKOheBf8yNHJaonC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103301LQtbyn9RU5T8F7Br.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/01/18/street-style-milan-mens-fashion-week-part-2/#slide-2\">这一届的米兰时装周上，场外也有一些不错的街头风格的示范</a>：&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103217pj1Xs6Cm5Vy2oiku.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103217OEL5UYaelB7IvyNF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701191032181Tox5Z6J0vCpuMSs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103218sp3ikX8zuvfqyQK4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103218LUwz19ATMYs3BQF5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103218M4vqQ2cuL9xbhCto.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103227Rm2jlx5peBM0GZE7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>为迎接 2 月 14 日情人节，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/issey-miyake-men-valentine-gift\">三宅一生男士出了一系列袜子</a>。特别将包装制成巧克力的模样，里面却是一双以“注染”染色技术制成、凹凸方式编织的波点袜子。这系列袜子将于 1 月 19 日开始正式于三宅一生贩售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103133b83laTG4cL1R9oBA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103146e1Rd6Jn2hMqoWBSm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103146ZVQBexW918sINU2p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>最近，时尚界流行起了一股奇怪的<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/ksenia-schnaider-denim/\"> Demi-Denims 牛仔裤潮流</a>。看似两条尺寸不一的牛仔裤叠加，实际上只有一条牛仔裤。上半部分有着宽松的廓形，下半部分收口较窄。这股风潮来自乌克兰品牌 Ksenia Schnaider，最近，在它的 2017 春夏系列中，也有多款 Demi-Denims 的单品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103022JKS95FhG4p76AMIP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103022rZjid4yY8hguJIFa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103022Bf3b8czHRroa74QI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103031UbGxc1vwXZpM0E8l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201701191030416rNOejSd35zJfKs7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103155yYk0c15xelAwGdXo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170119103204FNhjCpeYMdo4xPJa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/ksenia-schnaider-denim/\">popbee</a></p>"}